			<h3>Turn Window Shoppers into Customers with Browse Abandonment Campaigns</h3>
			<p>Track which products and categories customers are browsing, but haven’t yet added to cart, then <a href="http://rejoiner.com/resources/browse-abandonment-emails-turn-browsers-sales/" target="_blank">send them browse abandonment emails</a> showcasing viewed products, relevant top sellers and dynamically generated recommendations to get them back into buying-mode.</p>
		</div>
